<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>XV Años | Devany Estrella Velázquez Espinoza</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{

background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2b0148,#4b0082,#7b2cbf);

font-family:Arial,sans-serif;

color:white;

overflow-x:hidden;

}

header{

padding:70px 20px;

text-align:center;

}

header h1{

font-family:"Great Vibes",cursive;

font-size:65px;

color:#FFD700;

text-shadow:0 0 20px gold;

margin-bottom:15px;

}

header h2{

font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

font-size:28px;

color:white;

}

header p{

margin-top:20px;

font-size:20px;

}

.hero{

width:90%;

max-width:700px;

margin:auto;

border-radius:25px;

overflow:hidden;

box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(255,215,0,.45);

}

.hero img{

width:100%;

display:block;

}

section{

padding:50px 20px;

text-align:center;

}

.titulo{

font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

font-size:35px;

color:#FFD700;

margin-bottom:25px;

}

.card{

background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

padding:25px;

border-radius:20px;

max-width:800px;

margin:auto;

box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,.4);

}

.card p{

font-size:20px;

line-height:1.8;

}

.gold{

color:#FFD700;

font-weight:bold;

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>

<h1>Devany Estrella</h1>

<h2>Mis XV Años</h2>

<p>Con la bendición de Dios y de mis padres</p>

</header>

<div class="hero">

<img src="images/foto1.jpg">

</div>
